msgctxt "135	270"
msgid "Kido-san, hope you didn't wait long!\\nI was just out grabbing a few things!"
msgstr "Kido-san.\\nLo siento, fui de compras un rato."

msgctxt "281	393"
msgid "Oh, uh, it's all good.\\nSorry for bargin' in like this."
msgstr "Oh, perdóname a mí.\\nVine sin avisar."

msgctxt "453	575"
msgid "The chief's out on collection duty right now."
msgstr "El jefe está en media recolección en este momento."

msgctxt "580	694"
msgid "He should be back in just a jiff, though."
msgstr "No creo que tarde mucho, así que puedes esperar."

msgctxt "699	756"
msgid "Here, I'll pour you some tea."
msgstr "Te serviré un poco de té."

msgctxt "757	806"
msgid "You don't have to do that."
msgstr "No es necesario."

msgctxt "807	919"
msgid "So what brings you by?\\nForget something here?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿por qué estás aquí?\\n¿Olvidaste algo?"

msgctxt "925	1039"
msgid "Actually, there's this thing\\nI'm looking to run by Akiyama-san."
msgstr "En realidad, hay algo\\nque quería confirmar con Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "1044	1132"
msgid "I tried his cell and everything,\\nbut couldn't get through."
msgstr "Intenté llamarlo al celular,\\npero parecía estar apagado."

msgctxt "1137	1180"
msgid "Welcome to the club."
msgstr "¿Verdad que es molesto?"

msgctxt "1185	1393"
msgid "He always switches it off when he's out wandering.\\nSays he doesn't like people ruining his \"vibe.\""
msgstr "¡Siempre apaga el celular cuando toma un desvío\\npara jugar o hacer otras cosas que no sea trabajar!"

msgctxt "1398	1527"
msgid "It's a wonder anything ever gets done around here!"
msgstr "¡Por culpa de eso el trabajo nunca acaba, nunca acaba!"

msgctxt "1555	1628"
msgid "That's Akiyama-san for you."
msgstr "Típico de Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "1819	1924"
msgid "Don't think they're here for a loan..."
msgstr "No creo que ellos sean clientes..."

msgctxt "1929	2075"
msgid "Again?\\nYou guys are worse than roaches."
msgstr "¿Otra vez?\\nDe verdad que no aprenden la lección."

msgctxt "2080	2195"
msgid "Sorry, but you're going to have to leave."
msgstr "Disculpen, ¿podrían irse, por favor?"

msgctxt "2200	2450"
msgid "The chief isn't even here. Though if you really insist,\\nI'd be glad to kick you out myself."
msgstr "El jefe ni siquiera está aquí.\\n¡Pero si siguen insistiendo, yo me encargaré de atenderlos!"

msgctxt "2583	2643"
msgid "Look out, Hana-chan!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado, Hana-chan!"

msgctxt "2693	2753"
msgid "Hana-chan!"
msgstr "¡Hana-chan!"

